column2: select gal.ObjID, gal.u, gal.g, gal.r, gal.i, gal.z, gal.ra, gal.dec, s.z, l.h_alpha_eqw from galaxy gal JOIN specObj s on s.bestObjID = gal.ObjID JOIN galSpecLine l on l.specObjID = s.specObjID where gal.type = # AND gal.ra between # and # AND gal.dec between # and # AND s.z between # and #
